OL,5,COutlook for Sat 9 May to Mon 18 May
OL,6,FInitially, slowly-evolving weather
OL,7,Fpatterns are expected in the vicinity
OL,8,Fof the UK, with low pressure over
OL,9,Fwestern Europe and high pressure
OL,10,Fbuilding across or to the north of the
OL,11,FUK. Whilst largely settled conditions
OL,12,Fare likely in northern areas, there
OL,13,Fmay be some rain or showers across
OL,14,Fportions of England and Wales, which
OL,15,Fcould be heavy and locally thundery.
OL,16,FHowever, there is a slight chance
OL,17,Fthese wetter conditions could remain
OL,18,Fover the nearby Continent. Deeper into
OL,19,Fnext week and beyond, there may be a
OL,20,Ftendency for more widely unsettled
OL,21,Fconditions across the UK, with some
OL,22,Frain or showers at times. Whilst some
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Foccasional warm days are possible,
